Jarrod KAUFMAN, Rachel Kaufman, William Quick and Nancy Quick, on Behalf of Themselves and All Others Similarly Situated, Plaintiffs,
v.
LUMBER LIQUIDATORS, INC. and Robert M. Lynch, Defendants-Movants. M-872 September Term 2017
080001 Supreme Court of New Jersey. June 15, 2018

ORDER

It is ORDERED that the motion to strike portions of the Consumers League of New Jersey's proposed amicus brief is denied.
